##### `writable.write(chunk[, encoding][, callback])`

<!-- YAML
added: v0.9.4
changes:
  - version:
    - v22.0.0
    - v20.13.0
    pr-url: https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/51866
    description: The `chunk` argument can now be a `TypedArray` or `DataView` instance.
  - version: v8.0.0
